data.eml:eml: Three species of the isopod crustacean genus Antennuloniscus Menzies, 1962 (Asellota: Haploniscidae) from the Southern Ocean

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Brökeland, Wiebke (2006): Three species of the isopod crustacean genus Antennuloniscus Menzies, 1962 (Asellota: Haploniscidae) from the Southern Ocean. Zootaxa 1115: 1-29, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.171605
